## Notes for Development
- All images use Pexels URLs for consistency and performance
- Resume file should be kept updated in both `/public/` and `/dist/` directories
- SEO meta tags are comprehensive and should be maintained
- Brand consistency is crucial - maintain blue theme and professional tone
- Mobile responsiveness is priority - test on multiple devices
- Performance optimization is ongoing - monitor Core Web Vitals

